A small text-based adventure game I made when doing exercises for Learn Python The Hard Way by Zed A. Shaw.

To run, simply run 
python mini_text_game.py [YOUR NAME HERE] 
in mini_text_game.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTRUCTIONS/TIPS:


For info about current location and items, enter 'i' or 'info'.

Other navigation keywords may be figured out intuitively (left, right, forward, backward, ect.).

